  "Description": {
    "English": "An advanced upgrade for the starship's <span class=\"name name-technology\">landing system</span>, enabling the ship to land and take off from aquatic surfaces.<br><br>A mixture of bespoke jets and re-directed exhaust fans allow the ship to <span class=\"name name-stellar\">hover</span> just above the water's surface.",
